channel.title: Server wont go online please help! PLEASE!
channel.description:
Okay im finally decidinng to post after many hours of revising. i have a server i have a no-ip i have port forwarded i am running the server im logged on on my server but with a blank server
i try to put my server on the server status page but every time i try it's offline ??:S:S
I have been running it for more thann 2 hours but still says offline
any help would be gratefully appreciated
thanks in advance.
Goffy

item.title: Server wont go online please help! PLEASE!
item.dc:creator: @Johnnyboy93 Johnnyboy93
item.description:
@Johnnyboy93 wrote:

When you have no-ip downloaded, click the no-ip sign and turn your server on. If that doesn’t work, you may have to log into your router or modem. The same thing happened to me the other day, but i got my server to run. I hope i helped.
